org.jboss.windup.ast.java

Class ReferenceResolvingVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTVisitor
      • org.jboss.windup.ast.java.ReferenceResolvingVisitor

  • public class ReferenceResolvingVisitor
extends org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTVisitor
    Provides the ability to parse a Java source file and return a List of ClassReference objects containing the fully qualified names of all of the contained references. Note: A new instance of this visitor should be constructed for each CompilationUnit
    Author:
    Jesse Sightler, Lincoln Baxter, III
